
This is the administration panel for Loxim.

Installation instructions:

1. copy the files into the location suitable for your web server
2. insert the valid path to php into the first line of *.cgi in this directory
3. edit config.cgi
4. ensure you have the minimal php configuration:

[php]
short_open_tag = off
magic_quotes_gpc = off

5. make sure all the files have proper permissions (depending on your setup)
6. watch phpinfo() output by browsing pi.cgi, search for lxsbql

